\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\beta\mu\approx\rho V_{0}(z^{-1}+1)/2.\label{eq:mu-asymptotic-rism}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

To this end, one uses the convolution relation and the short hand notation
 
\begin_inset Formula $z=\rho\kappa/\beta$
\end_inset

