\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

kcal/mol.
 Although the ratio of two relaxation terms, solute polarization and solvent
 relaxation energies, is nearly constant for all solutes the value of this
 ratio differs notably from the intuitive linear electrostatic response
 limit.
 
\end_layout

